{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"表達式","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Expressions_and_Operators","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"表達式","title":"表達式","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>表達式</em>即任何有效的一組字面表達、變數、運算子、可求值的單一的值，值可以使用數字、字串、或邏輯值。</p>\n<p>大致上來說，表達式可分為兩種︰把值代入給變數，和單純的持有值。例如，表達式 <code>x = 7</code> 是把值 7 代入給 x 的表達式。表達式本身的求值結果是 7。這些表達式使用<em>代入運算子</em>。換句話說，表達式 <code>3 + 4</code> 單純的求值結果為 7，且沒有代入動作。這些表達式使用的運算子又可以簡單的稱為<em>運算子</em>。</p>\n<p>JavaScript 有以下幾種表達式︰</p>\n<ul> <li>算術式: 求出數值，例如，3.14159。（一般使用 <a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/算術運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/算術運算子\">算術運算子</a>。）</li> <li>字串式: 求出字元、字串，例如，\"Fred\" 或 \"234\"。（一般使用 <a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/字串運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/字串運算子\">字串運算子</a>。）</li> <li>邏輯式: 求出真值或假值。（通常和 <a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/邏輯運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/邏輯運算子\">邏輯運算子</a> 有關。）</li> <li>物件式: 求出物件。（參閱 <a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/特殊運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/特殊運算子\">特殊運算子</a> 取得有關求出物件的各種例子。）</li>\n</ul>\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/Unicode\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/運算子\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"表達式即任何有效的一組字面表達、變數、運算子、可求值的單一的值，值可以使用數字、字串、或邏輯值。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Expressions and operators","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/expressions_and_operators","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/expressions_and_operators/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"陣列的運用"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Expressions_and_Operators","title":"表達式"}],"pageTitle":"表達式 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}